These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
House: art-deco, modern, cape-cod, victorian, futuristic, colonial, cottage
1. the colonial house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the cottage house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the futuristic house is between the art-deco house and the cape-cod house##2
5. the victorian house is between the modern house and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| House   | cottage | cape-cod | futuristic | art-deco | victorian | modern | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, july, august, january, may, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in february##2
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Birthday   | june | november | february | august | january | july | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, rock, r&b, techno, trance, reggae, disco
1. the fan techno is on the right of the fan r&b##1
2. the fan reggae is on the right of the fan disco##1
3. the fan r&b is on the right of the fan electronic##1
4. the fan reggae is on the right of the fan disco##1
5. the fan rock is on the left of the fan electronic##1
6. the fan trance is between the fan reggae and the fan rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | reggae | trance | rock | electronic | r&b | techno |

