.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel, sports, superhero, family, martial-arts, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching family movies##2
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person watching sports movies##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel | superhero | adventure | family | disaster | sports |

