1. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growssunflower is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsazalea##2
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
6. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |  7   |
| Flower   | azalea | sunflower | zinnia | tulip | aconite | bellflower | balloon-flower |

